abstract: Rating the performance of U.S. players in an international friendly against Honduras on Oct. 8.
snippet: Rating the performance of U.S. players in an international friendly against Honduras on Oct. 8.
lead_paragraph: MIAMI GARDENS, Fla. -- Jurgen Klinsmann notched his first win as United States coach, the German-born midfielder Danny Williams got his first start for the Americans and Clint Dempsey scored his fourth U.S. goal -- a game winner -- of 2011.
